602B1|Longgacun   (Approved - N)}}, [[National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency|United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency]]</ref>; {{lang|ug|\u0644\u0648\u06ad\u06af\u0627 \u0643\u06d5\u0646\u062a\u0649}}<!--http://big5.cri.cn/gate/big5/wei6.chinabroadcast.cn/7466/more/20131/ZTmore20131.htm \u06af\u06c7\u0645\u0627 \u0646\u0627\u06be\u0649\u064a\u0649\u0633\u0649 \u0645\u06c7\u062c\u0649 \u0628\u0627\u0632\u0649\u0631\u0649 \u0644\u0648\u06ad\u06af\u0627 \u0643\u06d5\u0646\u062a\u0649 \u06cb\u06d5 \u0644\u06d5\u06ad\u06af\u06d5\u0631 \u0643\u06d5\u0646\u062a\u0649\u06af\u06d5 \u0686\u06c8\u0634\u0643\u06d5\u0646 \u062e\u0649\u0632\u0645\u06d5\u062a \u06af\u06c7\u0631\u06c7\u067e\u067e\u0649\u0633\u0649 \u0626\u0627\u067e\u062a\u0648\u0646\u0648\u0645 \u0631\u0627\u064a\u0648\u0646\u0644\u06c7\u0642 \u062c\u06c7\u06ad\u064a\u0649 \u062a\u06d0\u0628\u0627\u0628\u0649\u062a\u0649 \u062f\u0648\u062e\u062a\u06c7\u0631\u062e\u0627\u0646\u0649\u0633\u0649\u0646\u0649\u06ad ...--> / {{lang|zh-hans|\u9f99\u5c15\u6751}}), Langan ({{lang|zh-hans|\u5170\u5e72\u6751}}), Yingbage ({{lang|zh-hans|\u82f1\u5df4\u683c\u6751}}), Kuonasayibage ({{lang|zh-hans|\u9614\u7eb3\u8428\u4f9d\u5df4\u683c\u6751}}), Bashitiereke ({{lang|zh-hans|\u5df4\u4ec0\u94c1\u70ed\u514b\u6751}}), Hantuge ({{lang|zh-hans|\u6c57\u5410\u683c\u6751}}), Aziganbage ({{lang|zh-hans|\u963f\u5b5c\u5e72\u5df4\u683c\u6751}}), Gaziqiaka ({{lang|zh-hans|\u5c15\u5b5c\u6070\u5580\u6751}}), Muji ({{lang|zh-hans|\u6728\u5409\u6751}}), Kuonatugeman ({{lang|zh-hans|\u9614\u7eb3\u5410\u683c\u66fc\u6751}}), Sayi ({{lang|zh-hans|\u8428\u4f9d\u6751}}), Asa'er ({{lang|zh-hans|\u963f\u8428\u5c14\u6751}}), Kuonabazha ({{lang|zh-hans|\u9614\u7eb3\u5df4\u624e\u6751}}), Sayibage ({{lang|zh-hans|\u8428\u4f9d\u5df4\u683c\u6751}}), Ayagebagela ({{lang|zh-hans|\u963f\u4e9a\u683c\u5df4\u683c\u62c9\u6751}}), Bagela ({{lang|zh-hans|\u5df4\u683c\u62c9\u6751}}), Bashibagela ({{lang|zh-hans|\u5df4\u4ec0\u5df4\u683c\u62c9\u6751}}), Arejianggale ({{lang|zh-hans|\u963f\u70ed\u6c5f\u5c15\u52d2\u6751}})\n\n==Transportation==\n* [[China National Highway 315]]<ref name=\"1997xzqhguma\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Xinjiang]]\n[[Category:Township-level divisions of Xinjiang]]\n\n\n{{Xinjiang-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "\n\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See Template:Infobox Settlement for additional fields that may be available-->\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|name          =Muji\n|native_name = {{nobold|{{lang|ug|\u0645\u06c7\u062c\u0649 \u0628\u0627\u0632\u0649\u0631\u0649}}<br>{{lower|0.2em|{{lang|zh-hans|\u6728\u5409\u9547}}}}}}\n|other_name =\n|official_name          = \n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        =Town\n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline         =\n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          =\n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              =\n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              =\n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_type      =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           = \n|image_dot_map          =\n|dot_mapsize            =\n|dot_map_caption        =\n|dot_x =  |dot_y =\n|pushpin_map            =China Xinjiang\n|pushpin_label_position = \n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location in Xinjiang\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|pushpin_map1            =China\n|pushpin_label_position1 = \n|pushpin_map_caption1    =Location in China\n|pushpin_mapsize1        =\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = [[China]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Autonomous Regions of China|Autonomous Region]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Xinjiang]]\n|subdivis